hi, it is required in flexbox a pseudo state selector in order to know what is the css used value for box-orient

for example:

<box style="-moz-box-orient:vertical">

<tabbox style="-moz-box-orient:inherit;">
   <tabs style="-moz-box-orient:inherit;" id="test">
      <tab />
      <tab />
      <tab />
   </tabs>
</tabbox>

</box>

tabs#test:orient-vertical tab
{
    border-radius:5px 5px 0 0;
}

tabs#test:orient-horizontal tab
{
    border-radius:5px 0 0 5px;
}

Reproducible: Always

