hi David,
you mean for performance reasons?
i think that is really needed this, anyway

using current mozilla's flexbox i have had to make a script that writes an attribute on every element in order to use selectors like this:

tabs[usedorient="v"] tab
{
    border-radius:5px 5px 0 0;
}

tabs[usedorient="h"] tab
{
    border-radius:5px 0 0 5px;
}

i know it is a horror, but for me is the only solution

bye :)

