ok I understand...

and what about creating an event to observe flexbox orientation changes?

myel.addEventListener("flexboxOrientChanged",function(ev)
{
      if(ev.target!=this) return;

      // ...

},true);

it got the same risk of looping, circular depencies, etc,
but with javascript can be different, and it is not so different from:

window.onresize=function(){window.resizeTo(....);};

